  "StockRole": "Heavy Sniper & Defender",
  "YangsThoughts": "This variant of the Awesome is designed for units that cannot afford the newer, and more costly, variants or for older machines that, due to past damage, cannot be upgraded with the newer weapon systems and construction materials. The 9Q has a higher damage curve than previous models due to the inclusion of a fourth particle projectile cannon. Included into the design is also a Guardian ECM suite, making the design difficult to target with many of the newer weapon systems available to date. While the Awesome of past days were feared, this newest refit of the Awesome will strike fear into any warrior that crosses its path.",
